snippet.title: Escape from (Corp) LA | Callisto 6 | Season 1 Episode 7
snippet.description:
All hell has broken lose! In the dead center of enemy territory, the group has to fight for its life only to find another battle waiting for them afterwards: Do they make a deal with a villain or do they do something a little more... unpredictable?


Callisto 6 takes place in Los Angeles in the year 2119, where a world of cyberpunk is broken by the emergence of superheroes. 

Watch live on https://www.twitch.tv/geekandsundry Fridays at 4pm PT.
